simple present

Affirmative:

[I, you, we, they] [verbs] + [complemento]
[he, she, it] [verb 3p] + [complemento]

Negative:

[I you, we, they ] don't + [verb] [complemento]
[he, she, is] doesn't + [verb] [complemento]

Interrogative:

[Do] + [I, you, we, they] + [complemento]
[Does] + [he, she, it] + [complemento]

